data.description: Split level home on cul-de sac lot with plenty of parking space. Guest bedroom on the main floor, three bedrooms and two full baths on the upper floor and addition bedroom/ media room on the lower lever, sunroom, separate dining room. Private yard, large outbuilding in the back yard. Awesome location close to shopping markets, restaurants and more, located conveniently to both Scenic Hwy and Highway 78.
